*dmalloc-4.8.2-r1 (5 June 2002)

  5 June 2002; Jon Nelson <jnelson@gentoo.org> dmalloc-4.8.2-r1.ebuild:
  
  Fixed to use --enable-threads and --enable-shlib instead of --with-shlib
  (Closes 3238)

